act: Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Act
subject: Appointment of a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation
precis: Approval of the appointment by the Minister of Infrastructure and Communities of Rita Virk of Calgary, Alberta, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure on a part-time basis, for a term of four years.
